Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,THE STEADY ADVANCE OF JUSTICE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark portal closed since ancient times...\NI command you to open!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.58,0:02:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.79,0:02:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Check that out!\NThe gate opened like it's welcoming us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.80,0:02:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Come everyone. Let us go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.43,0:02:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.81,0:02:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Dai?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.02,0:02:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.15,0:02:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now... with all my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.11,0:02:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm truly glad that you came to help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.28,0:02:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Me and my dad had to work together\Nto shatter a door like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.37,0:02:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just wracking my brain\Nthinking about how to shatter this door.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But you showed us that\Nthere was another way to open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:02:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.30,0:03:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.14,0:03:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark King Ban's way of\N"might makes right" is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.27,0:03:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank to you, I can truly believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.56,0:03:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.52,0:03:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Being powerless can be a problem,\Nbut power isn't everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.61,0:03:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowledge and strength of heart\Nare forms of power, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.53,0:03:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Come. The true battle lies ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.49,0:03:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We should hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.79,0:03:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! They all got inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's crush this bug\Nand follow them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:03:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.60,0:04:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that the real father figure is back,\NI can stop playing the older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.61,0:04:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I can be a warrior again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.86,0:04:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you babbling on about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.03,0:04:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.25,0:04:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It means I can cut loose\Nwithout worrying about the consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring everything you've got!\NToday I feel no fatigue!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.76,0:04:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,His second time today?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Grand Cross!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.78,0:04:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,None shall pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I expected the castle of\Nan evil Dark King to be more gloomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.33,0:04:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is like a high-class palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more luxurious than any castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.51,0:05:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But its path is too linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.76,0:05:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two reasons\Nto build a palace like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Firstly, it displays its beauty\Nin a set route.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.14,0:05:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Secondly, if anyone should ever invade,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it forms a single path\Nthat can be ambushed from either side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.74,0:05:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This place looks magnificent...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...but Master Aban is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.87,0:05:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a single path the whole way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel will cut off any pursuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Our issue is how to defeat\Nenemies in our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Time out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.47,0:05:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't keep up! I'm exhausted again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.23,0:06:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm out of Magic Power\Nand running drains any stamina I regain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,\NPopp's been exhausted the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.11,0:06:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you exhausted, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.66,0:06:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah. Running just gave me more energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How does his body work?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please gimme a healing spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm dying here! Don't abandon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How about I end your suffering with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.72,0:06:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.68,0:06:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That settles it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a break over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.31,0:06:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.60,0:06:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,In the enemy castle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.77,0:06:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I see my services\Nmay be required, King Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.28,0:06:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:06:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot leave things\Nto Mystban and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.37,0:07:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it is time you called upon\NBan Palace's most powerful guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.05,0:07:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My King!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.19,0:07:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured that we would need\Nthis picnic set I brought!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.15,0:07:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What sort of situation was he expecting?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, what is up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly saying we should\Ntake a break in the enemy castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel's still out there\Nfighting alone you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be in bad shape,\Nbut I'm not about to rest here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.42,0:07:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Master, what are you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.43,0:07:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My Magic Power's restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a different feather from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a Gold Feather for attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It uses the Shining Stone,\Na simplified gem of Kiseiseki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.36,0:08:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an item for amplifying\Nthe impact of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.95,0:08:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And what I just used on Popp was this,\Na Silver Feather for healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.42,0:08:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The gem is made from Holy Stone,\Nand can store Magic Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The Magic Bullet Gun I gave Maam\Nuses the same gem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then a stone that possesses\Nboth properties is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.76,0:08:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. The Kiseiseki\Nin your Insignias of Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But Kiseiseki takes time to mature\Neven after its completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I was only able to create these two types\Nof Feathers in the Cave of Trials.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.74,0:08:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:09:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, it looks like your Magic Power\Nhasn't fully been restored yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.83,0:09:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.83,0:09:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This Feather contains enough Magic Power\Nto fully restore up to three normal Mages,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.54,0:09:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's completely empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When did I get that strong?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like you've grown\Nin power a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How about another jab for good measure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.22,0:09:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, no thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.73,0:09:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But I insist!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.89,0:09:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Healing up and readying yourself\Nis an important duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It may hurt a little, but it must be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,To refuse would be an insult\Nto those out there fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.54,0:09:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Maam. Use these\Nto restore everyone's Magic Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.75,0:09:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And heal their stamina with Healing Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.21,0:09:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir. But what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.63,0:09:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take the time to go ahead for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.34,0:10:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There should be\Nmore powerful traps laid ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get rid of them while I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.14,0:10:11.82,On Top,,0,0,0,,TRAP-SMASHER HAMMER
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.81,0:10:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll also map out the castle's layout.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it dangerous alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.36,0:10:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Princess Leona.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.11,0:10:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you be so kind as to assist me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.79,0:10:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam, look after the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.34,0:10:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. We'll be back in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay put even after you finish healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You can enjoy the meal that I prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.52,0:10:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's heal up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be the meal he meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.49,0:11:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. He's still the same Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It feels like\Nhe'll take care of Ban himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,0:11:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get complacent\Njust because Master Aban's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.33,0:11:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We should assume we'll be fighting\Nwithout him like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.79,0:11:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, we should heal up\Nlike he told us to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.26,0:11:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll be ready to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.01,0:11:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That way, Master won't have to\Nrisk his life for us again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.60,0:11:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get this over with then!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But can we avoid\Nthe jabs to the head this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's stick to the arm, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.57,0:11:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Like there's a difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.95,0:11:51.50,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4}ABAGAMU{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:56.50,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4}MINAKATOR{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.84,0:12:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Aban,\Nwhat exactly do you need me for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.09,0:12:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, Minakator is\Nthe only Purifying Spell I can cast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have time\Nto attain any of the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.68,0:12:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.35,0:12:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought you along for one reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.23,0:12:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to have these.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.86,0:12:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You've giving these to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I believe you can take my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.29,0:12:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.46,0:12:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Mystban!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.42,0:12:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It... It wasn't supposed to be like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.03,0:13:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Underworld monsters\Nweren't that tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.07,0:13:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We've beaten them!\NNow you're all that's left!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.16,0:13:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You underestimated us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.12,0:13:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, your Underworld monsters\Nwere just a pack of beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't know how to coordinate\Nor work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.79,0:13:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like the humans here\Nhave a greater sense of purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In... In that case, I'll have to have\NMystban fight the humans!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can use that opportunity\Nto escape from here!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.57,0:13:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's my only choice!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Mystban!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.99,0:13:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! I beg of you!\NShow your great power!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,With our legion of monsters defeated,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:14:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,your power is all we can count on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.67,0:14:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall return to Ban Palace\Nand protect King Ban!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime,\Nyou can crush these fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.97,0:14:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're certainly clutching at straws,\Naren't you, Zaboera?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't defeat these fools, what\Ncan you do against Dai in Ban Palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.70,0:14:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're arguing?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,When you reap what you sow
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.24,0:14:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,they say it always comes\Nwhen you are at your lowest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.21,0:14:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You've come a long way\Nby using others for your benefit,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.42,0:14:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but at the very end,\Nyou chose the wrong target.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.88,0:14:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall return to Ban Palace\Nand protect King Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.01,0:14:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I am under no obligation\Nto offer my help to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:14:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Mystban!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.81,0:15:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Try doing things yourself for once!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.69,0:15:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Zaboera...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,either way, if you return to Ban Palace\Nwith no results, you will be executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,At least try to deal with these humans and\Ntheir Magic Circle of Light by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.79,0:15:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps such efforts from a worm like you\Nwill change King Ban's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Mystban... no, Mystban!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.01,0:15:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.76,0:15:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We're both former Legion Commanders!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.98,0:15:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we were comrades\Nwho fought together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How can... How can you\Nabandon me like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.07,0:15:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,"Comrades..."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.86,0:15:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're finally resorting to\Nthe platitudes of the servants of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.08,0:15:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But Zaboera...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:16:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,if we're such close friends as you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.75,0:16:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,then you should know all too well\Nwhat I would say in this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.42,0:16:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,"Th-The Dark King's words..."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.22,0:16:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly, "...take precedence above all."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.23,0:16:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's been abandoned!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.35,0:16:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Zaboera used countless warriors\Nto further his own ambitions.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.69,0:16:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, for the first time,\Nhe himself has been cast aside.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.28,0:16:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.29,0:16:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Mystban!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.16,0:16:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I aren't through yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.92,0:16:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to run like a coward?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You can believe that if it suits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.63,0:16:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't many in this world\Nwho can fight me on equal ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.05,0:17:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.06,0:17:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You are an impressive one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.44,0:17:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe if you had fought at full strength,\Nour battle wouldn't have taken so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.36,0:17:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the same could be said for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.28,0:17:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mystban...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.87,0:17:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell, Ron Berku. And you humans\Nwith your unexpected mettle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.54,0:17:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I respect anyone with powerful bodies\Nand minds, be they ally or enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise to remember\Nyour achievements this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's one ally here\Nthat he never respected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Zaboera, you're all out of options.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.23,0:17:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you return to Ban Palace\Nyou'll be executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.57,0:17:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That said, you're not stupid enough\Nto think you can beat all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.03,0:18:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,0:18:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.09,0:18:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What a joke! What a sick joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.63,0:18:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,To have the poster boy of stupidity\Ncall me stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.02,0:18:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you're so magnanimous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.77,0:18:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that I wasn't\Nable to use Mystban!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.82,0:18:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But unlike all of you, I always\Nprepare a backup plan when I enter battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.49,0:18:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have ways to fight\Nwithout soiling my own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.37,0:18:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The hundreds of monsters here\Nwill protect me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.79,0:18:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid! Your damn monsters\Nare all half-dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.09,0:19:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Half-dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.27,0:19:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. We can't have that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.02,0:19:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A spell?! Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't have that.\NWe can't have that at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard! How can you slaughter\Nyour servants like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.09,0:19:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You fools wouldn't understand.\NI need them as corpses.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.93,0:19:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Need them... as corpses?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.72,0:19:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the parts to my final weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.19,0:19:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Parts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Superior Being Synthesis!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.01,0:20:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I've long considered\Nwhat the ultimate power up could be!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.02,0:20:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Superior Beings are incredibly powerful,\Nbut they deplete life energy too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.36,0:20:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll convert others,\Nbut I'd never become one myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.74,0:20:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My wish is to have the ability\Nto remain completely unharmed
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.54,0:20:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,while moving freely at will\Nand easily crushing my enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.63,0:20:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-The mindset of a scoundrel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.92,0:21:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the result!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.60,0:21:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Superior Being Number Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.14,0:21:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I should call it\Na Superior Being Zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.27,0:21:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A Superior Being Zombie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.19,0:21:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So I guess you're just trying\Nto use size as an advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.44,0:21:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think that sort of play will work!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.66,0:21:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.79,0:21:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for that mighty blow, Ron Berku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.80,0:21:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You've confirmed my hypothesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.88,0:21:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the ultimate Superior entity!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.26,0:21:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron Berku overwhelmed Mystban!\NAnd yet his blade...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.60,0:21:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...doesn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.08,0:22:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.08,0:22:17.71,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.58,0:22:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I gaze at you from behind\Nas you begin to walk away{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.58,0:22:28.26,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}arukidasu kimi no ushirosugata wo nagameru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.26,0:22:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.26,0:22:36.06,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.85,0:22:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We act tough and follow our hearts{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.85,0:22:45.28,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}massugu de tsuyogari na sonna bokura ga{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.44,0:22:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And we began this tale together{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.44,0:22:49.70,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hajimeta monogatari{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.20,0:22:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Beyond the horizon something glimmers{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.20,0:22:56.00,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}chiheisen no mukou de kirameiteiru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.16,0:23:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've been seeking something certain{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.16,0:23:02.38,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tashika na mono sagashitsuzukete iruno{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the distant sky, dancing in the wind{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:09.22,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}haruka sora ni kaze ni nori matte{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.38,0:23:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The birds sing as though\Nilluminating the future{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.38,0:23:15.01,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tobu tori wa naiteita mirai wo terasuyouni{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.18,0:23:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promise that connects us\NThe adventure we share{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.18,0:23:20.81,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wo tsunagu yakusoku to\Nbokura de tsumugu bouken wo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.98,0:23:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Again in this world{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.98,0:23:26.98,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mata kono sekai de{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.74,0:23:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cornered, Zaboera turned into\Na Superior Being Zombie.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.79,0:23:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With a body of concentrated monsters,\Nnot even Ron Berku's blade can cut it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.04,0:23:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just as it seems that the tables\Nhave turned in the battle of Loroi Valley,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.71,0:23:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nova, against the protest of those\Naround him, faces off with Zaboera.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.39,0:23:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.85,0:23:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Other Hero"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.72,0:23:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i}
